snippet.textDisplay: I think what makes the hair not blend is how shiny it is. This is a common problem, and you can reduce the shine of hairpieces in several ways. For cosplay wigs, ive soaked them in a lil bath of fabirc softener for a few days and then brushed them through with cornstarch. Ive tried shampoo instead, but it doesnt work as well. For something thats clipped into your hair, dry shampoo might help make it look more matte and blend better.
